Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说阿姆斯特朗少将与雷文中将的失踪有关联？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她不会干留下证据的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢 我们的工作只是掌握这要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁那女狐狸在中央被虎群包围的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是少将阁下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 没想到你竟会在中央当差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了什么后门？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是靠实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛头小子真是大言不惭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您今日来是有何要事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统阁下叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定暂时回不了北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有机会务必和我吃个便饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你请客？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到你破产也无所谓我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 真是没胆又没钱的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我送您点花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央有很多不错的花店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 阿姆斯特朗少将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问一下雷文中将失踪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是瞒不了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下您这样贤明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何身边会有那样粗心大意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就把他收拾掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不需要那种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种口风不紧的人对阁下没好处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将对你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的军团 我国的成立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及阁下的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本没问 他就自顾自全说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听了这些话还乖乖来见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我是来接收那白痴的位子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 这个位子就给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换 布里格斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我的手下接管了 可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里都是我精心培育的精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下一定会满意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我中意你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奋力挣扎吧 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少将亲自入了虎穴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这里也被他们占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他们还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使主君不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然是团结在同一意志下行动的一枚巨石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是布里格斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 接下来就是熊虎之争了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近来工作还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙得连吃饭时都得努力赶工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要学的东西很多 还算比较忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过幸好阁下工作速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是不会偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来话题走向不大愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说斯卡现在去北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟也在北方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方有和我同期的露茜和伊安在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们告诉我不少消息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 记得春天北方军和东方军有联合演习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 迈尔斯少校和巴卡尼亚上尉总让我们吃败仗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯 巴卡尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约克 艾达 修格都受邀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈勃克 奥斯卡 迈克 尤尼 诺拉 查理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又是尤尼和露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着尤尼 最后是斯塔林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞利姆·布拉德雷是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么不可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央到底在搞什么阴谋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能稍微吃惊一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃惊了你给我什么好处？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 胆子够大这点我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是问号码 问你真正的名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没啦 我是奴隶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有权利和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被视为所有物让渡买卖的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让渡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是把财产 权利等物转让给他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是你这种人让我诞生的 真想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你吗 给我血的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来好像是要做实验 被抽了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你给的血液 我才能降生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…叫23号还是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你起个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢帅气一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥…迪奥弗拉斯托斯·波姆巴斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太长啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？哦对了 太长你记不住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为笨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准说我笨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就冯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯·霍恩海姆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯·霍恩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点倒是能记住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼写是…对了你会读书写字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会才怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会也能干活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶的活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不想得到自由和权利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想得到人类的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想一辈子当奴隶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是和永远困在这烧瓶里一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我赐给你知识吧 冯·霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你到底是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么称呼你才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧瓶中的小人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就叫我Homunculus（人造人）吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事万物都诞生于一 回归于一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即所谓 一即是全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全来自一 一中有全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若一中无全 全即为无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经是出色的炼金术师了 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还只是个助手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本比不上主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你给了我知识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能过上这样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也感谢主人的提拔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天结婚成家也不是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真是不便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样保持社群进行繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法存续种族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说什么繁殖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你看来可能很可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有家庭有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人类才会感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你的幸福又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒不奢求什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从这烧瓶里出来就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么达到权利和荣耀顶峰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会追求这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是在陛下面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆敢犯上我就把烧瓶摔碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想要毁掉未知的知识之源吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别啰嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长生不老 到底能否实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衰老的焦虑吗 真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克塞尔克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就教你们长生不老的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是灌溉用的水道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王下令在全国铺设水路网
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是克塞尔克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们平民也关怀备至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好 一个不留全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧把血之纹刻上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北边村子被袭击了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是一个活口都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这之前是西边的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁干的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下期待的炼成阵已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漫长啊 终于好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这样就可以长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王可以长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是划时代的瞬间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是长生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我们在中心不会被波及的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成阵真正的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你所站的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己体内你的血打开了门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血脉相容的亲人 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你我就是一切的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅西蒂尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱茵迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尼 梅悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 所有人的魂魄都被抽走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 您没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…我自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据你的血的信息 我做了自己的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 终于可以用自己的脚走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是人造人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事 你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你提供血液的回报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给了你名字 给了你知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 还给了你不朽的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不朽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在心中集中意识试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你成为不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为代价的这个国家所有人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过其中一半我用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你的协助 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你就是爱德和阿尔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没想到你竟是我儿子们的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 你太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹密女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹密 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就拿药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微懂点医术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希格先生 请去叫辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹密女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到真理了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你牺牲了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内脏被取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要唤醒死去的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹密 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刺穿了你的肚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我呼吸顺畅多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被取走的内脏是你的罪证 所以拿不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我稍微整理了一下你的内脏系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让血液循环顺畅一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹密女士 你现在还不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆 你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有名为冯·霍恩海姆之人形的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲学者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上石 大炼金药
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石 就像它有很多名字一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其形态也不一定是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科先生拿的是半液体状的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利拿的是矿石状的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小大概这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为说是具有巨大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为会更大才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.99,0:23:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没见过比小石头更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.41,0:23:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果是很大的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就需要不计其数的人来当材料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是尽量不想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获得什么 必须付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是炼金术之原理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是人世的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.19,0:24:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第41话 地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真在少年身上寻求的代价便是伤痛
